• RequestWorker
The RequestWork class that handles requests starts a separate thread for each incoming request.

Step 4: Define the Servlet interface
• CloudServlet
• StaticViewServlet
The CloudServlet interface is implemented by defining a StaticViewServlet that handles static resources. 
The static resource handler will automatically intercept requests under static paths.

